ActSpecial Import Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Import Measures Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL IMPORT MEASURES REGULATIONS in order to (1) properly reflect the enabling authority for certain provisions of the Regulations; (2) improve the consistency of the English and French versions of the Regulations; and (3) properly reflect the current organizational structure of the Canada Border Services Agency.
